data.description: This exquisite home offers an array of luxurious features for your comfort and enjoyment. Nestled on a private lot with open views of the Green River Gamelands, the home combines elegant design, modern amenities, and an open floor plan that's perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. From the spacious outdoor patio, entertain poolside gatherings, or unwind in the hot tub. Large windows flood the home with natural light. The kitchen is equipped with a gas AGA stove for the culinary enthusiast, granite counters, soft close cherry cabinetry, and large pantry. Home and saltwater pool are backed up by Generac whole house generator. Ample storage can be found throughout, along with unfinished attic space perfect for the hobbyist. Energy saving features include an encapsulated crawl space and blown in foam insulation. Explore the outdoors along the trails throughout the private community or a picnic by the lake. Private well installed in addition to community well access.
